              <span class="text-2xl">🌀</span>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-600">Didattica</p>
                <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-655 transition">Postura e Fisiologia</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">La base formativa dell'Accademia: comprendi i meccanismi intimi del corpo umano.</p>
